7238508534", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39001725_3751167241841867_2951941851866511973_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=VYvHmcH0yNoQ7kNvgFmbT5I&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCzSp2H0QjD_MQY1mtJCLJan2QlyU8rhKfRG9kQr5uZUQ&oe=670E585D"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "cover.png", "id": "1691892224915749", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75580056_1691892228249082_8993988736869608245_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=FdAUJDVJKBcQ7kNvgFaPIoi&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBJ0PjjNrwHE5JJdBr3v-8b_aLR3xAbvloLVJiZC6-ZCw&oe=670E59DA"}, "display_name": "Stealthy Swipers", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Description:\nImmerse yourself in the thrilling world of \"Stealthy Swipers,\" a cutting-edge VR game where your mission is to \"borrow\" valuable items from a vast, high-tech environment while evading detection by the colossal room owner. This game combines intense stealth mechanics, strategic gameplay, and a rich, futuristic setting to deliver an unforgettable virtual reality experience.\n\nGame Features:\n\n    Immersive VR Environment:\n        Experience a meticulously crafted, enormous space brought to life with state-of-the-art VR graphics. The game environment is designed to be visually stunning and deeply immersive, making you feel like you are truly inside a high-tech, futuristic world.\n\n    Stealth and Strategy Gameplay:\n        Engage in challenging stealth gameplay that requires careful planning and quick reflexes. Utilize shadows, create diversions, and use high-tech gadgets to avoid being detected by the vigilant room owner.", "short_description": "Description:\nImmerse yourself in the thrilling world of \"Stealthy Swipers,\" a cutting-edge VR game where your mission is to \"borrow\" valuable items from a vast, high-tech environment while evading detection by the colossal room owner. This game combines in